   Sort Method: quicksort  Memory: xxxkB
   ->  Custom Scan (DocumentDBApiExplainQueryScan) (actual rows=2 loops=1)
         namespaceName: mkpq_db.mkpq_coll_a3
         indexName: a_b_1
         indexKey: {"a": 1,"b": 1}
         isMultiKey: true
         multiKeyPaths: a
         indexBounds: ["a": [1, 1], "b": [1, Infinity]]
         innerScanLoops: 3 loops
